item.title: Hyperon/Project Annialation help
item.dc:creator: @Native1 Native^
item.description:
@Native1 wrote:

  1. Delete the project files eclipse generates.
  2. Create a new Java Project if it.
  3. Click the problems button in the low left corner.
  4. Select all the problems the occur, and press delete.

Then it should work.
